                    <ab>Die quintodetjmo mensis februarii, inditjone detjma, in <geogName
                            ref="#estates/2470"><placeName>Pupiniano</placeName></geogName>. <rs
                            key="#Venditio">Vendi[tjo</rs> fe]tjt <persName><name ref="Albertinus"
                                >Albertinus</name></persName> filiu quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Zantus">Zanto</name></persName> venditore vobis <persName><name
                                ref="Sigitia">Sigiza</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Imilda">[Ime]lda</name></persName> germane emtritjs, idest
                        totam et integram eam partem de me[dieta]te de <rs key="#Casalia"
                            >casali</rs> da <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Casalia #Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3639">Sancti Martini qui vocatur in <geogName
                                ref="#estates/2471">Gardiliana</geogName></orgName>. Albertus
                        calegario et Petrus de Ganduzo, Martinus Balbo et Iohanne Bocune et
                        Pasquale.</ab>
